body:
Dear @jart, I still think it's not a problem for StackOverflow.

I checked again and found that the `tf_op_files.txt` file contains only:
```
tensorflow/core/ops/random_ops.cc
tensorflow/core/ops/random_grad.cc
```

And missing this: `tensorflow/core/kernels/random_op.cc`

After adding the missing line, it can load the model now
